## Performance Targets

Aim for these Lighthouse scores before any production deploy:

| Metric         | Target  |
| -------------- | ------- |
| Performance    | ≥ 90    |
| Accessibility  | ≥ 90    |
| Best Practices | ≥ 90    |
| SEO            | 100     |
| LCP            | < 2.5s  |
| CLS            | < 0.1   |
| FID/INP        | < 200ms |
